{
  "texts": [
    "Hash operation is performed to obtain the public key y i,0 = H(x i,0), y i,1 = H(x i,1).",
    "These keys can be visualized as two-dimensional arrays:",
    "• Now we can publish the public key(pk 0, pk 1) for everyone.",
    "For example, we can send a public key to a friend, embed it in a certificate, or publish it on Keybase.",
    "• We then use the key to sign the l-bit message M."
  ]
}